978. The odds may be against Portugal but this hasn’t stopped them in the past. <img class="alignnone wp-image-831373 size-large lazyload" title="Cristiano Ronaldo lifts the Euro 2016 trophy following the UEFA EURO 2016 Final match between Portugal and France at Stade de France on July 10, 2016 in Paris, France." src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-1024x649.jpg" alt="Cristiano Ronaldo lifts Euro 2016 trophy with Portugal" width="1024" height="649" data-srcset="https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086.jpg 1024w, https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-300x190.jpg 300w, https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-768x487.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"><img class="alignnone wp-image-831373 size-large lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" title="Cristiano Ronaldo lifts the Euro 2016 trophy following the UEFA EURO 2016 Final match between Portugal and France at Stade de France on July 10, 2016 in Paris, France." src="https://i0.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-1024x649.jpg?resize=1024%2C649&#038;ssl=1" alt="Cristiano Ronaldo lifts Euro 2016 trophy with Portugal" width="1024" height="649" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086.jpg 1024w, https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-300x190.jpg 300w, https://www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-768x487.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/GettyImages-545947086-1024x649.jpg?resize=1024%2C649&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAA